  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b8e\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd:     \u0b93\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b8e\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "EPS Interim General Secretary: Abolition of OPS",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Following the permission of the Madras High Court to hold a general meeting of the Anna Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam (ADMK), a resolution has been passed to select former chief minister and opposition leader Edappadi Palaniswami as the interim general secretary of the ADMK.",
        "A special resolution was also introduced and O. Panneerselvam and his supporters were removed from the party's basic membership.",
        "OPS Officials seal the ADMK head office in Rayapetta, Chennai, which supporters seized in the morning. 144 Prohibitory Order has been issued in that area. The police are concentrated there."
      ],
